    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive overall shape. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept smoke-free; the leather upholstery is supple and the electronics function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule including a recent full synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. With plenty of tread remaining on the premium tires and a smooth-shifting transmission, this car offers a reliable and high-quality driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
