    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in great shape for all your upcoming adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved, runs smooth, and is ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
