    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This high-revving powerplant benefits from individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, providing a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been serviced, addressing the primary technical concerns of the E46 chassis. The suspension features upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers for sharpened turn-in and reduced body roll. While the Titanium Silver finish shows minor stone chips and the interior displays slight bolster wear, the mechanical health is excellent. Equipped with a limited-slip M Variable Differential, this M3 remains a benchmark for analog driver engagement.",
